No. —, Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Clarence H. Venner, Petitioner. Submitted January 14, 1924. Decided January 21, 1924. Mr. Elijah N. Zoline for petitioner. Mr. J. P. Blair, Mr. Wm. F. Herrin and Mr. Garret W. McEnerney for respondent.

Motion for leave to file a petition for a writ of mandamus herein denied..
